  "texts": [
    "The freed human time may also incur new unexpected environmental costs.",
    "In this section, we examine the environmental impact of AI and human illustrators in the context of creating visual content.",
    "In this section, we analyze the environmental impact of AI-generated illustrations.",
    "We examine two prominent AI image generation engines: DALL-E2 and Midjourney.",
    "DALL-E2 is based on an underlying GPT-3 engine (similar to ChatGPT above), and Midjourney is based on a system called stable diffusion."
  ]
